<BaseLayout
  title="Kanha Barasingha 2026 - The Swamp Deer Conservation Success Story"
  description="The complete story of Barasingha (swamp deer) at Kanha National Park. Population recovery from 66 to 800+, hard-ground subspecies, conservation history, and where to see them."
  keywords="kanha barasingha, swamp deer kanha, hard ground barasingha, kanha deer species, barasingha conservation"
